---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Privacy Policy — InfoOnVisa" noindex={true}>
  <div class="wrap prose">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="muted">Last updated: 21 June 2026</p>

    <h2>1. What we collect</h2>
    <p>We collect minimal, non-personal usage data (such as the routes searched) to improve the service. We do not require sign-up and do not collect your name or contact details.</p>

    <h2>2. Cookies &amp; advertising</h2>
    <p>We may use cookies for basic functionality and analytics. We use Google AdSense to show ads; Google and its partners may use cookies to serve ads based on prior visits. You can opt out via Google’s Ads Settings.</p>

    <h2>3. Third parties</h2>
    <p>Advertising and affiliate partners may process limited data per their own privacy policies. We don’t sell your personal data.</p>

    <h2>4. Your choices</h2>
    <p>You can disable cookies in your browser. For ad personalisation controls, see Google’s Ads Settings and the EU/EEA consent tools where applicable.</p>

    <h2>5. Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions about this policy or your data? Email us at <a href="mailto:contact@infoonvisa.com">contact@infoonvisa.com</a> or visit our <a href="/contact">Contact page</a>.</p>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .prose { max-width: 720px; padding: 40px 20px; }
  .prose h1 { font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .prose h2 { font-size: 19px; margin: 24px 0 8px; }
  .prose p { margin-bottom: 10px; }
</style>
